{"tid":1451724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日塞機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:54:24.000Z","uid":217866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5cc9d5ef90d7cee0cde89c8d9f1410a72583de","tid":1451724,"uid":217866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:19:22.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n***<br />\n無得參與塞機場既巴絲 麻煩用紗布/眼罩/膠布/任何嘢遮右眼 我地要既係noise 要令班黑警抬唔起頭做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac252bd2a957e78902f7a11527f8c0defabef462","tid":1451724,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:19:54.000Z","msg":"【幫手推】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac053d4f25760807285f12f9a980e297abac8829","tid":1451724,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:54:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場文宣整合post</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450351</a><br />\n<br />\n「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場"}]}